# CI checks before completing work

When you create or edit code in this repo:

1. Run `pnpm prettier --write` on every file you touched.
2. Run `pnpm check` and fix any failures before responding.
3. Do not commit unless the user explicitly asks.

Prettier config (`.prettierrc`): semicolons, single quotes, trailing commas, print width 100.
